	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nuper unas ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> literas recepi datas ad dominum <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesnerum</persName>, quas ut tradas rogo.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bellum inter <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> gliscit; nam <persName ref="p8375" cert="high">Anglię</persName> regina <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotos</placeName> vicinos et coniunctos propter religionem susceptam a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> oppugnatos indefensos relinquere non vult.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam sub prętextu religionis bellum ceptum a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> in totius insulę suppressionem directum est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniarum</placeName> quoque rex sub hiis spetiosis titulis, nempe hęreseos et rebellionis in armorum societatem adducitur immemor antiquissimorum fęderum et sępius acceptorum benefitiorum a priscis et nostri ęvi <persName ref="p8375" cert="high">Anglię</persName> regibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germanos</placeName> veros et memores sui officii spes est non militaturos in hoc nefando bello <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallo</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetii</placeName> quoque detrectarent impia arma induere et gladios in innoxios stringere, nihil regem pręclari perfecturum verismile esset.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Regina et terra et mari suas copias admovit ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotiam</placeName>, et nisi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallię</placeName> rex ęquissimas conditiones et accipiat et det, regina Scotię libertatem armis asserere annitetur.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De reginę connubio nihildum accepi; maior natu <placeName type="citizen_name">Suetię</placeName> regis in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName> adventurus dicitur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orator Cesaris ibidem quoque hęret; verum an exorator [fu]turus sit, plęrique dubitant.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur reginam inter horrida <persName type="auto_name">Martis</persName> arma tristes hymenęos facere nolle, ne liberatori magis necessitate coacta nupsisse quam delecto coniugi dicatur.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Religio in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> fęlices successus habet, qui ut quotidie magis fęlices sint, deus implorandus est.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quęso, ut me commendes d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyri</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene valeas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentinę</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Fragment von <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121" cert="high">Monts</persName> Hand.]</note>
					<note>[Datum: Vgl.: <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121" cert="high">Mont</persName> an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">HB</persName>, 20. Feb. und 13. Juli 1560. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">HB</persName> an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8009" cert="high">Fabricius</persName> 12. und 19. Juli 1560.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
